\newlabel{fig:interpolated_cubic_cubic}{{3}{3}{Re-interpolated Lagrangian data (Approach~B, scheme 2). Left: rise velocity. Right: circularity. Both Lagrangian curves (blue) now closely track the Eulerian reference (red).\relax }{figure.caption.3}{}}
